### List active donation events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events
Accept: application/json

### Create donation event (without auth, should fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Winter Relief Campaign",
  "description": "Helping families through the winter",
  "active": true,
  "goalAmount": 5000
}

### Create donation event
POST http://localhost:8080/api/events
X-API-Key: dev-api-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Winter Relief Campaign",
  "description": "Helping families through the winter",
  "active": true,
  "goalAmount": 5000
}

### Donate to event
POST http://localhost:8080/api/events/1/donate?donorName=George&email=george@test.com&amount=25
X-API-Key: dev-api-key
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

